snippet.title: Dungeon Dev promotional video [English]
snippet.description:
Under the Demon Lord's orders, following a secret deal with the human kingdom, you must create a special dungeon that will satisfy the kingdom's heroes.
Strategically place monsters and traps according to the roles of the heroes, such as "Tank," "Dealer," and "Healer," to design this unique dungeon!

Launch on Steam on November 15, 2024

steam link : https://store.steampowered.com/app/2872750/Dungeon_Dev/
X : https://x.com/EttuTeam
